ight and it had a female- apparently Russian, sat on the stool smiling- but I am married so after a brief scan of the bar I relaxed in the area outside the bar absorbing the atmosphere.Overall, I had a great experience here and would recommend it to anyone looking for a bit of luxury. Of cousre they have a free transfer to the Hiton Jumeriah Beach whereyou can enjoy the beach etc.	
